01:09:17.314 --> 01:09:21.278
This is how we become unfamiliar with the

01:09:21.337 --> 01:09:23.779
heritage of language and are so easily

01:09:23.859 --> 01:09:24.378
deceived.

01:09:24.399 --> 01:09:26.520
It's why I went to such lengths to

01:09:26.581 --> 01:09:29.382
write not only amplified translations of

01:09:29.462 --> 01:09:32.944
the Hebrew text from the oldest extant

01:09:32.965 --> 01:09:34.586
witnesses of the Dead Sea Scrolls,

01:09:34.985 --> 01:09:38.148
but I provided the very basis of the

01:09:38.188 --> 01:09:40.270
Hebrew words that were being translated so

01:09:40.289 --> 01:09:41.789
you become familiar with them and can look

01:09:41.850 --> 01:09:43.070
them up for yourselves and would

01:09:43.131 --> 01:09:44.051
understand the etymology.

01:09:44.311 --> 01:09:45.296
etymology of words,

01:09:45.556 --> 01:09:46.801
because if you don't understand the words,

01:09:46.820 --> 01:09:49.409
you have no chance of knowing who's

01:09:49.430 --> 01:09:50.193
telling you the truth.

01:09:52.301 --> 01:09:54.421
So while Christians will protest that

01:09:54.822 --> 01:09:56.943
something which heals and is beneficial is

01:09:57.002 --> 01:09:58.363
by definition good,

01:09:58.844 --> 01:10:01.085
and that a message can be news,

01:10:01.404 --> 01:10:03.425
there is no reason to extrapolate when the

01:10:03.485 --> 01:10:05.525
primary meaning is readily apparent.

01:10:06.127 --> 01:10:06.587
Therefore,

01:10:06.926 --> 01:10:08.887
those who seek to know and share the

01:10:08.908 --> 01:10:10.988
truth are compelled to translate

01:10:11.088 --> 01:10:13.949
euangelion accurately so that others will

01:10:14.029 --> 01:10:15.970
understand its intended meaning.

01:10:16.390 --> 01:10:16.791
Further,

01:10:17.150 --> 01:10:20.332
there was nothing beneficial or good about

01:10:20.412 --> 01:10:21.512
Sha'uwl's message.

01:10:22.132 --> 01:10:25.253
which is why Yahowah called him the plague

01:10:25.293 --> 01:10:25.753
of death.

01:10:26.953 --> 01:10:28.074
Now, along these lines,

01:10:28.154 --> 01:10:30.954
if agelos meant news as opposed to

01:10:31.175 --> 01:10:31.676
message,

01:10:32.076 --> 01:10:34.855
the agelos or spiritual messengers would

01:10:34.895 --> 01:10:38.356
be newscasters instead of Yah's spiritual

01:10:38.436 --> 01:10:40.757
envoys and representatives and his

01:10:41.217 --> 01:10:42.177
heavenly messengers.

01:10:42.439 --> 01:10:42.798
However,

01:10:42.838 --> 01:10:45.238
while you can be translated as good,

01:10:45.319 --> 01:10:46.380
beneficial, and healing,

01:10:46.720 --> 01:10:49.380
there is a far more accurate and

01:10:49.520 --> 01:10:51.060
descriptive definition.

01:10:52.077 --> 01:10:55.417
In Hebrew, a messenger is a Malak.

01:10:56.097 --> 01:10:59.179
A herald of news is a Basar.

01:10:59.719 --> 01:11:02.359
Towb means good and beneficial.

01:11:02.659 --> 01:11:04.640
El is one of Yahowah's titles.

01:11:04.860 --> 01:11:06.421
Eld is testimony.

01:11:06.801 --> 01:11:07.240
Further,

01:11:07.701 --> 01:11:11.601
King Sha'uwl was good while King Dowd was

01:11:11.702 --> 01:11:12.082
right.

01:11:14.002 --> 01:11:15.622
Which do you suppose matters?

01:11:16.524 --> 01:11:17.344
Being right.

01:11:17.703 --> 01:11:18.884
And God's terminology?

01:11:19.805 --> 01:11:21.104
Paul's or the church's?

01:11:23.636 --> 01:11:24.216
You have a choice.

01:11:24.796 --> 01:11:28.319
I don't think it's a hard choice.

01:11:28.380 --> 01:11:29.961
So even in Greek,

01:11:30.280 --> 01:11:32.903
if the intent was to communicate good as

01:11:32.922 --> 01:11:34.104
in a sense of good news,

01:11:35.014 --> 01:11:37.537
The preferred Greek words for good are

01:11:37.577 --> 01:11:40.380
kalos and agathos.

01:11:40.420 --> 01:11:42.521
Further, in the Sermon on the Mount,

01:11:42.601 --> 01:11:45.284
the speaker is translating using the

01:11:45.364 --> 01:11:49.167
former in Matthew, five sixteen saying, Thusly,

01:11:49.208 --> 01:11:51.411
let your light shine before men,

01:11:51.751 --> 01:11:54.634
so they might see within you the responses

01:11:54.713 --> 01:12:00.942
and endeavors which are good . Kalos

01:11:57.636 --> 01:11:59.880
thereby wonderfully attributing them to

01:11:59.920 --> 01:12:00.961
your heavenly Father.

01:12:01.542 --> 01:12:04.564
And with the latter gospel, Jesus says,

01:12:05.246 --> 01:12:11.073
I am good in Matthew, using Agathos.

01:12:11.908 --> 01:12:12.248
Therefore,

01:12:12.349 --> 01:12:14.729
I present Yahowah's perspective on what is

01:12:14.829 --> 01:12:15.711
actually Towb.

01:12:16.150 --> 01:12:17.572
Good, productive, and beneficial.

01:12:17.652 --> 01:12:19.472
I'd be remiss if I didn't share the

01:12:19.512 --> 01:12:22.154
