01:12:27.555 --> 01:12:29.077
hundred and fifth Psalm,

01:12:29.377 --> 01:12:32.037
which actually proclaims because they

01:12:32.118 --> 01:12:34.840
focus upon and observe closely examining

01:12:34.880 --> 01:12:37.301
and carefully considering his clearly

01:12:37.341 --> 01:12:39.742
communicated prescriptions of what they

01:12:39.761 --> 01:12:41.542
