01:12:42.042 --> 01:12:43.123
and his Towrah,

01:12:43.503 --> 01:12:45.885
his source of teaching and instruction.

01:12:46.426 --> 01:12:51.828
They are saved, radiating, he has light.

01:12:51.868 --> 01:12:52.109
Mizmowr

01:12:52.149 --> 01:12:56.251
Song, Psalm, one oh five forty five.

